the start of the Korean War, but the protesters also demanded that 
Washington punish some of the U.S. veterans involved and compensate 
the victims' relatives. ``It is a sad tragedy that the revelation 
about the massacre should come to light so late,'' said Yu 
Jin-jeong, who led a group of about 50 demonstrators. 

</P>
